public class UbySemanticFieldResource
extends org.apache.uima.fit.component.Resource_ImplBase
implements de.tudarmstadt.ukp.dkpro.core.dictionaryannotator.semantictagging.SemanticTagProvider

This shared resource can be added as ExternalResource in Analysis Engines that annotate common nouns, main verbs and adjectives with semantic field information from WordNet (for English text) or GermaNet (for German text).

Author:
Judith Eckle-Kohler
